        @Nullable
public static java.lang.String checkModList​(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> listData,
                                            Side side)
        参数:
        listData - map of modId string to version string, represents the mods available on the given side
        side - the side that listData is coming from, either client or server
        返回:
        null if everything is fine, returns a string error message if there are mod rejections
